oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Benefit Concert at the Nashville Municipal Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: fund raising;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue on yellow) announcing a Benefit Concert featuring Willie Nelson, Kenny Rogers, Patty Loveless, Gary Morris, Ricky Van Shelton, Eddie Rabbitt, T. Graham Brown, K. T. Oslin, Exile, and The Oak Ridge Boys at the Nashville Municipal Auditorium on April 22. Proceeds from the concert go to the Reba McEntire Band Family Fund.
